title: Tutorial
description: The perfect guide for an aspiring mercenary who is desperate need of cash, and is willing to dive into a huge maze and fight potentially life threating foes

data.text:
Welcome! Welcome my dear mercenary!
You have been hired to retrieve some very important items for me!
Unfortunately, these... items... appear to be at the center of some quite huge labrynths strewn across the world, filled to the brim with deadly creatures.
The good news is I have prepared a little mock battle for you, to test your skills before venturing into the deep.

Use W A S and D to move
